H5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"Bom Sa Ho&agrave;ng xuất hiện trong bối cảnh Chiến tranh Lạnh căng thẳng giữa Li&ecirc;n X&ocirc; v&agrave; Mỹ. Về mặt kỹ thuật, thiết kế ban đầu nhắm tới sức c&ocirc;ng ph&aacute; 100 megaton, nhưng khi thử nghiệm người ta điều chỉnh để đạt khoảng 50 megaton nhằm giảm bụi ph&oacute;ng xạ\" width=\"625\" height=\"352\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em>Bom Sa Ho&agrave;ng xuất hiện trong bối cảnh Chiến tranh Lạnh căng thẳng giữa Li&ecirc;n X&ocirc; v&agrave; Mỹ. Về mặt kỹ thuật, thiết kế ban đầu nhắm tới sức c&ocirc;ng ph&aacute; 100 megaton, nhưng khi thử nghiệm người ta điều chỉnh để đạt khoảng 50 megaton nhằm giảm bụi ph&oacute;ng xạ</em></p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:350px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"Quả bom c&oacute; khối lượng xấp xỉ 27,000 kg v&agrave; d&agrave;i khoảng 8m, buộc kh&ocirc;ng qu&acirc;n Li&ecirc;n X&ocirc; phải d&ugrave;ng m&aacute;y bay n&eacute;m bom chiến lược Tu-95 được cải tiến để mang theo.\" width=\"625\" height=\"350\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em>Quả bom c&oacute; khối lượng xấp xỉ 27,000 kg v&agrave; d&agrave;i khoảng 8m, buộc kh&ocirc;ng qu&acirc;n Li&ecirc;n X&ocirc; phải d&ugrave;ng m&aacute;y bay n&eacute;m bom chiến lược Tu-95 được cải tiến để mang theo.</em></p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <div class=\"video-native photo [&amp;_video]:max-h-[80vh] [&amp;_video]:h-full\" width=\"625\" height=\"350.8928571428571\" style=\"width:625px;height:350.8928571428571px;max-height:80vh\">\n    <video playsinline=\"\" muted=\"\">\n     <source src=\"https://gif-baomoi.bmcdn.me/w700_r1/2025_10_31_106_53641124/fdb7d6318a7863263a69.gif.webm\" type=\"video/webm\"></source>\n     <source src=\"https://gif-baomoi.bmcdn.me/w700_r1/2025_10_31_106_53641124/fdb7d6318a7863263a69.gif.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></source>\n    </video>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em>Vụ nổ ph&aacute;t s&aacute;ng mạnh đến mức b&oacute;ng tối ban đ&ecirc;m bị x&oacute;a mờ ở h&agrave;ng trăm km, v&agrave; s&oacute;ng xung k&iacute;ch l&agrave;m vỡ k&iacute;nh cửa sổ ở nhiều khu vực xa trung t&acirc;m.</em></p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <div class=\"video-native photo [&amp;_video]:max-h-[80vh] [&amp;_video]:h-full\" width=\"625\" height=\"350.8928571428571\" style=\"width:625px;height:350.8928571428571px;max-height:80vh\">\n    <video playsinline=\"\" muted=\"\">\n     <source src=\"https://gif-baomoi.bmcdn.me/w700_r1/2025_10_31_106_53641124/654441c21d8bf4d5ad9a.gif.webm\" type=\"video/webm\"></source>\n     <source src=\"https://gif-baomoi.bmcdn.me/w700_r1/2025_10_31_106_53641124/654441c21d8bf4d5ad9a.gif.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></source>\n    </video>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em>Về chiến lược, bom Sa Ho&agrave;ng đặt ra 3 th&ocirc;ng điệp r&otilde; r&agrave;ng. Thứ nhất, đ&oacute; l&agrave; biểu hiện sức mạnh tinh hoa của chương tr&igrave;nh hạt nh&acirc;n Li&ecirc;n X&ocirc;.</em></p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <div class=\"video-native photo [&amp;_video]:max-h-[80vh] [&amp;_video]:h-full\" width=\"625\" height=\"343.75\" style=\"width:625px;height:343.75px;max-height:80vh\">\n    <video playsinline=\"\" muted=\"\">\n     <source src=\"https://gif-baomoi.bmcdn.me/w700_r1/2025_10_31_106_53641124/bd059883c4ca2d9474db.gif.webm\" type=\"video/webm\"></source>\n     <source src=\"https://gif-baomoi.bmcdn.me/w700_r1/2025_10_31_106_53641124/bd059883c4ca2d9474db.gif.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></source>\n    </video>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em>Việc tr&igrave;nh diễn sức nổ khổng lồ kh&ocirc;ng chỉ nhằm mục ti&ecirc;u qu&acirc;n sự đơn thuần m&agrave; c&ograve;n l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng cụ ch&iacute;nh trị để &eacute;p Mỹ v&agrave; c&aacute;c đồng minh phải t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n lại c&aacute;n c&acirc;n răn đe.</em></p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <div class=\"video-native photo [&amp;_video]:max-h-[80vh] [&amp;_video]:h-full\" width=\"625\" height=\"343.75\" style=\"width:625px